==MOBO Awards==
The [[MOBO Awards]] (an acronym for "Music of Black Origin") were established in 1996 by [[Kanya King]]. They are held annually in the [[United Kingdom]] to recognize artists of any race or nationality performing music of black origin. 50 Cent has received three awards.

{| class="wikitable"
|-
